ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR APPLE APP STORE DISTRIBUTION:

This software includes integration with Apple frameworks (HealthKit, WidgetKit, etc.)
subject to Apple's terms and conditions. Use of this software to create applications
for distribution on the Apple App Store requires:

1. Valid Apple Developer Program membership
2. Compliance with Apple's Human Interface Guidelines
3. Acceptance of Apple's App Store Review Guidelines
4. Proper privacy disclosures as required by Apple

The privacy-by-design architecture of this software (on-device only, no data
collection) is a core feature. Any modifications that introduce data collection,
tracking, or off-device transmission must:

1. Update the Privacy Policy and App Store privacy labels
2. Obtain explicit user consent
3. Comply with applicable privacy laws (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)

For questions about licensing or commercial use, please contact the project
maintainers.
